high_descs: Turn around and go to the table.
Pick up the butter knife on the table.
Turn around and go to the other side of the table.
Put the knife in the coffee cup on the table.
Pick up the coffee cup on the table.
Turn and go to the counter by the sink.
Put the coffee cup in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Move the coffee cup from the table to sink.

high_descs: Walk towards the recycling bin and then turn right towards the table.
Pick up the knife in front of the bottle on the table.
Turn left, walk towards the dishwasher, turn right towards the fridge, and then turn right to find a cup on the table.
Put the fork in the cup.
Pick up the cup with the fork from the table.
Turn right and walk towards the toaster on the counter to your right.
Place the cup in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup with a fork in front of the toaster on the counter.

high_descs: Go straight towards the trash can, then turn right to go to the table.
Pick up the butter knife on the table, located in front of the soap.
Turn left, go straight, turn right to go around the table, go straight toward the fridge, turn right, move forward, then turn right to face the table.
Put the butter knife in the mug, on the table.
Pick up the mug from the table
Turn right, then go to the counter above the dishwasher.
Place the mug on the counter, in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a butter knife in it on the counter.

high_descs: turn towards your right and approach the center island
pick up the knife on the counter
go to the exact opposite side of the island
put the knife into the cup
turn towards the counter next to the sink
approach the counter in front of the toaster
set the mug with knife inside in front of the toaster
anns.task_desc: place the mug with the knife inside on the counter in front of toaster
